[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":368},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230425\u002F1940966356\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230425\u002F1940966356\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230425\u002F1940966356\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230425\u002F1940966356\u002F":344,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20230425\u002F1940966356\u002F":353},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2023\u002F04\u002F25\u002Fdeploy-express-to-vercel\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":328,"date":329,"description":25,"extension":330,"lang":331,"meta":332,"navigation":333,"path":334,"readingMinutes":335,"seo":336,"standalone":337,"stem":338,"tags":339,"tldr":341,"updated":329,"url":342,"__hash__":343},"content\u002FNodejs\u002FExpress-部署到-Vercel.md","Express 部署到 Vercel","1940966356",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":322},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,29,32,59,62,67,77,82,85,91,94,100,103,109,119,122,127,130,154,160,166,169,178,185,188,267,270,277,283,286,292,301,304,318],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Vercel","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FHFmqtfp.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"這一篇記錄一下關於 Express 部署到 Vercel 的一些事項跟狀況。",[20,27,6],{"id":28},"express-部署到-vercel",[12,30,31],{},"首先這邊我使用的 Express 是透過 Express Generator 來產生的，指令如下：",[33,34,39],"pre",{"className":35,"code":36,"language":37,"meta":38,"style":38},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","express --view=ejs express-vercel\n","bash","",[40,41,42],"code",{"__ignoreMap":38},[43,44,47,51,55],"span",{"class":45,"line":46},"line",1,[43,48,50],{"class":49},"s_sBn","express",[43,52,54],{"class":53},"sCcAr"," --view=ejs",[43,56,58],{"class":57},"sTRMh"," express-vercel\n",[12,60,61],{},"所以結構大概是這樣",[12,63,64],{},[15,65],{"alt":50,"src":66},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F59hLusV.png",[12,68,69,70,76],{},"接著我們要做的事情就是把這個專案部署到 ",[71,72,17],"a",{"href":73,"rel":74},"https:\u002F\u002Fvercel.com\u002Flogin",[75],"nofollow"," 上面，所以請你先打開 Vercel 的網站並且登入，這邊我選擇使用 GitHub 登入",[12,78,79],{},[15,80],{"alt":17,"src":81},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FIp21rin.png",[12,83,84],{},"接著因為我本身有使用過 Vercel，所以我直接點選右上角的 New Project，如果你是第一次使用的話，你會看到這個畫面",[12,86,87],{},[15,88],{"alt":89,"src":90},"New Project","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FDw3htsD.png",[12,92,93],{},"接著搜尋一下專案名稱，然後點選 Import",[12,95,96],{},[15,97],{"alt":98,"src":99},"Import","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fv3gDvoz.png",[12,101,102],{},"接著就是依照需求填寫 Project Name 跟設定 Environment Variables，這邊我們不需要設定 Environment Variables，所以就直接點選 Deploy",[12,104,105],{},[15,106],{"alt":107,"src":108},"Deploy","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FLHar1tf.png",[110,111,112],"blockquote",{},[12,113,114,118],{},[115,116,117],"strong",{},"Note","\n你會發現 Framework Preset 沒有支援 Express 或者是 Node.js 這是正常的。",[12,120,121],{},"基本上部署速度非常快，所以一下子之後你就會看到畫面跳轉到這邊來了",[12,123,124],{},[15,125],{"alt":107,"src":126},"https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002F3Pc8Rzh.png",[12,128,129],{},"接著當你到你這個專案的控制台，可以看到 Visit 按鈕，當你點進去你會發現畫面寫著",[33,131,133],{"className":35,"code":132,"language":37,"meta":38,"style":38},"404: NOT_FOUND Code: NOT_FOUND ID: hkg1::z24c5-1682413583568-853a71174389\n",[40,134,135],{"__ignoreMap":38},[43,136,137,140,143,146,148,151],{"class":45,"line":46},[43,138,139],{"class":49},"404:",[43,141,142],{"class":57}," NOT_FOUND",[43,144,145],{"class":57}," Code:",[43,147,142],{"class":57},[43,149,150],{"class":57}," ID:",[43,152,153],{"class":57}," hkg1::z24c5-1682413583568-853a71174389\n",[12,155,156],{},[15,157],{"alt":158,"src":159},"404: NOT_FOUND","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FKh9cbuu.png",[12,161,162,163,165],{},"雖然我們已經可以成功部署 Express 到 Vercel 上，但實際上還有一些東西要處理，否則你會發現不管你怎麼用都是 ",[40,164,158],{},"。",[20,167,168],{"id":168},"解決方案",[12,170,171,172,177],{},"那麼該怎麼解決呢？雖然有找到一篇 ",[71,173,176],{"href":174,"rel":175},"https:\u002F\u002Fvercel.com\u002Fguides\u002Fusing-express-with-vercel",[75],"Using Express.js with Vercel","，但這一篇跟我們的情況不太一樣，因為這一篇主要是針對 API 的，但是我們的專案會有頁面，所以才不適用。",[12,179,180,181,184],{},"但是我們可以發現關鍵的東西，也就是 ",[40,182,183],{},"vercel.json"," 這個檔案，這個檔案是用來設定 Vercel 的，所以我們可以透過這個檔案來解決我們的問題。",[12,186,187],{},"那內容該寫什麼呢？只需要這樣寫",[33,189,193],{"className":190,"code":191,"language":192,"meta":38,"style":38},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{\n  \"builds\": [{ \"src\": \"app.js\", \"use\": \"@now\u002Fnode\" }],\n  \"routes\": [{ \"src\": \"(.*)\", \"dest\": \"app.js\" }]\n}\n","json",[40,194,195,201,234,261],{"__ignoreMap":38},[43,196,197],{"class":45,"line":46},[43,198,200],{"class":199},"sMAXC","{\n",[43,202,204,208,211,214,217,220,223,226,228,231],{"class":45,"line":203},2,[43,205,207],{"class":206},"sKpQp","  \"builds\"",[43,209,210],{"class":199},": [{ ",[43,212,213],{"class":206},"\"src\"",[43,215,216],{"class":199},": ",[43,218,219],{"class":57},"\"app.js\"",[43,221,222],{"class":199},", ",[43,224,225],{"class":206},"\"use\"",[43,227,216],{"class":199},[43,229,230],{"class":57},"\"@now\u002Fnode\"",[43,232,233],{"class":199}," }],\n",[43,235,237,240,242,244,246,249,251,254,256,258],{"class":45,"line":236},3,[43,238,239],{"class":206},"  \"routes\"",[43,241,210],{"class":199},[43,243,213],{"class":206},[43,245,216],{"class":199},[43,247,248],{"class":57},"\"(.*)\"",[43,250,222],{"class":199},[43,252,253],{"class":206},"\"dest\"",[43,255,216],{"class":199},[43,257,219],{"class":57},[43,259,260],{"class":199}," }]\n",[43,262,264],{"class":45,"line":263},4,[43,265,266],{"class":199},"}\n",[12,268,269],{},"然後再一起部署到 Vercel 上面，就可以看到畫面正常顯示了。",[110,271,272],{},[12,273,274,276],{},[115,275,117],{},"\nVercel 會自動偵測你的專案 Commit，所以你可以不用再手動部署。",[12,278,279],{},[15,280],{"alt":281,"src":282},"Express","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FkQh22Es.png",[12,284,285],{},"而且原本無法戳的 API 也都可以戳了",[12,287,288],{},[15,289],{"alt":290,"src":291},"API","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002FDBhrkHN.png",[12,293,294,295,300],{},"而關於這個檔案的說明，你可以在 ",[71,296,299],{"href":297,"rel":298},"https:\u002F\u002Fvercel.com\u002Fdocs\u002Fconcepts\u002Fprojects\u002Fproj